### SAM2 model weights (optional, downloaded at runtime)

When SAM2 is enabled the application downloads ONNX model weights at runtime
from Hugging Face (g-ronimo/sam2-tiny). These weights are derived from Meta's
Segment Anything Model 2, licensed under the **Apache License 2.0** by Meta
Platforms, Inc.

SAM2 repository: https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything-2

You must comply with Meta's Apache 2.0 license when using or redistributing
these model weights.

### ONNX Runtime (optional, native builds only)

When built with `--features sam2` on native targets, the `ort` crate
automatically downloads ONNX Runtime binaries from Microsoft. ONNX Runtime
is licensed under the **MIT License** by Microsoft Corporation.

ONNX Runtime repository: https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime
